Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:15.59,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}Chain reaction
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:19.51,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}見つめる Red eye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:24.18,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}真理を探していたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:28.52,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}あてもなく彷徨いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:35.11,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,1300)\blur3\be3}幾千億の絡み合う Elements
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.15,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}思考の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:39.86,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}揺れている Chaotic town
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:42.16,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}まるで so Confusion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.32,0:00:44.20,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}消えないんだ　Spiritual pain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.53,0:00:47.58,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,1300)\blur3\be3}Where do we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:51.71,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}光と闇が無限に揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:56.05,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}天使が悪魔と踊ります
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:01:00.43,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}時を越えたDNAの記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:01.80,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}Key of the light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:06.31,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}真理はすぐそこに
