Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:15.59,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}Chain reaction
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:19.51,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}注视着你 Red eye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:24.18,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}一直在寻找真理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:28.52,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}却在彷徨中迷失了方向
